36
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:28,900
I suppose

37
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:31,540
you have your reasons, Your Majesty.

38
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:34,220
The imperial court requires

39
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:37,980
a balance.

40
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:39,940
But now,

41
00:02:40,380 --> 00:02:42,380
two powerful generals

42
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,020
seek to unite.

43
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:47,140
How could I

44
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:50,700
rest easy with this?

45
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:54,820
Their grievances were predictable.

46
00:02:58,579 --> 00:02:59,660
Since that's the case,

47
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:04,140
I shall

48
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:06,220
make their division

49
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:08,660
