50
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,020
Your Majesty,

51
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:17,060
General Fengyun requests an audience.

52
00:03:26,290 --> 00:03:29,980
(Xiao Mansion)

53
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:33,260
Your wedding gown
was rushed to completion.

54
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:34,220
It just arrived.

55
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:36,579
Quickly try it on.

56
