58
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,300
Come on.

59
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:42,940
Come.

60
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,420
The embroidery and fabric

61
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,540
are truly first-rate.

62
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,100
Huaijin is thoughtful.

63
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,420
But this dress looks so complicated.

64
