How do I wear it?

65
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,500
Don't worry.

66
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:01,380
We'll help you.

67
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,380
Go try it.

68
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:17,540
Miss He looks stunning.

69
00:04:18,579 --> 00:04:19,940
Huaijin chose well.

70
00:04:20,380 --> 00:04:21,700
In Yaojing, these past years,

71
