75
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:34,100
Rongwei.

76
00:04:34,140 --> 00:04:34,980
Miss He.

77
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,340
Huaijin has returned.

78
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,340
Let him try his attire alone.

79
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,180
Right now,

80
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:42,780
he shouldn't see
the bride's full ensemble.

81
