82
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:59,220
Xiao Jue.

83
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:06,580
Is anything wrong?

84
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:09,780
He Yan, heed the decree.

85
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,980
His Majesty

86
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:20,820
decrees that

87
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,180
He Yan,

88
00:05:22,300 --> 00:05:23,260
a scholar and warrior,

89
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,580
has done great feats,

90
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,060
protecting Jiyang,

91
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,140
defending Rundu,

92
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:28,860
and repelling Wutuo.

93
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:30,580
For her contributions,

94
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,620
she is granted
the Mansion of General Feihong.

95
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:37,500
May she continue
exceeding my expectations

96
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:39,060
with tireless dedication

97
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:40,980
and loyalty.

98
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,340
- Thank...
- Another edict.

99
00:06:02,940 --> 00:06:04,500
General Feihong,

100
00:06:05,380 --> 00:06:06,220
He Yan,

101
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:08,620
has noble character

102
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,180
and dual expertise.

103
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,900
Lord Shijin's son,

104
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:15,940
Chu Zhao, Vice Director

105
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:17,420
of the Secretariat,

106
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:19,260
has honorable bearing

107
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:21,860
and exceptional talent.

108
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:23,780
They are

109
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:26,220
a most fitting match.

110
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:28,260
By imperial decree,

111
00:06:28,740 --> 00:06:29,980
the two shall wed

112
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:33,260
(Imperial Edict)
on a day

113
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:34,900
of good fortune.

114
00:06:38,659 --> 00:06:39,620
That's all.

115
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:44,740
He Yan narrowly escaped death

116
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,620
to reclaim the General Feihong title.

117
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:50,020
Forcing her to abandon it

118
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:51,860
would erase

119
00:06:52,340 --> 00:06:53,260
her very essence.

120
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:55,900
The Xiao Army

121
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:59,180
is my father's life's work

122
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,980
and remains my duty.

123
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,220
Let me let go.

124
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,340
Then I

125
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:08,860
cannot remain myself.

126
00:07:11,220 --> 00:07:12,060
It seems

127
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:14,620
you've made your choice.

128
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:17,980
You left me no other choice.

129
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:23,020
I shall have you perform another task.

130
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,940
This marriage decree.

131
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:27,940
You shall personally deliver.

132
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,100
No,

133
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:40,980
I won't.

134
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:42,540
You are defying my order?

135
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,100
Please

136
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,500
punish me.

137
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:54,460
You...

138
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,340
Aren't you afraid of

139
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,940
dragging down your family?

140
00:08:34,539 --> 00:08:35,780
If that's your order,

141
00:08:38,940 --> 00:08:40,380
I obey.

142
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:55,100
What did you say?

143
00:08:58,820 --> 00:09:00,180
Repeat that.

144
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:10,700
You broke plum branches

145
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,220
and made bridal attire for me.

146
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:17,540
In the end,

147
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:21,780
you want me to marry someone else.

148
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:28,510
♪Walking through the crowd,
without asking about the future♪

149
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:34,400
♪Wandering half a lifetime,
solitary as the moon♪

150
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,580
If that's the case,

151
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:38,740
I...

152
00:09:40,740 --> 00:09:41,700
accept...

153
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:47,140
