00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:32,030
♪My love rests between your fingers♪

162
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:36,670
♪Farewell tears blur my vision♪

163
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:39,700
♪Indescribable yearnings♪

164
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,900
General Fengyun,

165
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:43,940
