166
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:52,820
How else should I

167
00:10:54,300 --> 00:10:55,820
accept this decree gratefully?

168
00:11:01,430 --> 00:11:05,120
♪Before destiny is sealed♪

169
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:07,740
♪Again and again♪

170
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:14,370
♪My love for you burns fiercely♪

171
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:18,880
♪Lifelong devotion turns into a vow♪

172
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:22,110
♪That's my last wish♪

173
00:11:23,110 --> 00:11:29,160
♪Awaiting the spread of moonlight♪

174
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:39,100
(As the General Feihong,)

175
00:11:39,980 --> 00:11:41,380
you must soar freely

176
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,020
in the sky.

177
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:05,060
The Emperor

178
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:08,540
summons General Feihong to the palace.

179
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:24,830
(Devoted to Duty, Open to Counsel)

180
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:28,700
This is He Yan.

181
00:12:29,060 --> 00:12:29,900
Your Majesty.

182
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:31,460
At ease.

183
00:12:36,820 --> 00:12:37,660
Miss He,

184
00:12:38,940 --> 00:12:41,420
I know you and Mr. Xiao
share mutual affection.

185
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,660
But

186
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,380
Mr. Chu is also an outstanding talent.

187
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:47,700
He'll soon rise
to first-rank official status.

188
00:12:49,860 --> 00:12:50,700
Your Majesty,

189
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:51,860
however great he is,

190
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:53,500
it is irrelevant to me.

191
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:54,860
I come today

192
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:58,460
to request you to revoke that decree.

193
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:09,220
Your Majesty.

194
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:10,660
At ease.

195
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,060
Perfect timing.

196
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:14,420
She wants me to retract my decree,

197
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,420
but it's inappropriate.

198
00:13:18,660 --> 00:13:19,500
Your Majesty,

199
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:21,780
I will cherish He Yan wholeheartedly

200
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:23,940
and make her understand my sincerity.

201
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:25,020
Given time...

202
00:13:25,020 --> 00:13:26,020
This is unnecessary.

203
00:13:29,260 --> 00:13:30,100
Your Majesty,

204
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,340
I know

205
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,420
you just want to prevent

206
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:35,780
a marriage between two military leaders.

207
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:39,580
I won't marry Xiao Jue.

208
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:43,180
But

209
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,500
I won't marry Chu Zhao either.

210
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,660
Outrageous!

211
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:50,940
Please calm your anger.

212
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:52,420
I

213
00:13:52,620 --> 00:13:53,540
won't defy the decree,

214
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,020
but I refuse to settle.

215
00:13:57,940 --> 00:14:00,060
If I can't spend my life
with the one I love,

216
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,180
I would rather

217
00:14:02,940 --> 00:14:04,060
remain alone forever.

218
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,620
Please grant me.

219
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:14,820
Your Majesty,

220
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:18,860
if He Yan

221
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:20,940
refuses to marry Chu Zhao,

222
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,540
I implore you

223
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:27,900
to grant her

224
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:30,740
a choice.

225
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:43,300
Fine.

226
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:48,140
Have it your way.

227
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,340
I shall

228
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:00,460
take my leave.

229
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,460
(Have I)

230
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:19,180
(truly erred?)

231
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:25,820
Were you involved in

232
00:15:27,580 --> 00:15:28,580
this arranged marriage?

233
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:32,820
Yes.

234
00:15:34,660 --> 00:15:35,620
I requested it.

235
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,900
But Xiao Jue still dumped you.

236
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:45,780
You're an intelligent man.

237
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,020
You should understand

238
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:50,460
that decree cannot constrain me.

239
00:15:51,180 --> 00:15:52,260
We were never

240
00:15:53,980 --> 00:15:55,420
in the cards.

241
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:57,700
There's no future

242
00:15:58,260 --> 00:15:59,540
for you two.

243
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:02,100
Why not turn your eyes to me?

244
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:03,220
Can you not tell

245
00:16:03,220 --> 00:16:04,580
my heart is as true as his?

246
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:05,700
That's not love.

247
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:08,900
It was all a calculated game.

248
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,780
Should I cut open my heart?

249
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:17,140
Is a calculated heart any less worthy?

250
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,260
Tell me!

251
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:19,500
You're insane!

252
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:22,780
How much ambition is hidden

253
00:16:24,780 --> 00:16:26,620
behind the love you speak of?

254
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,620
Was every single thing you did

255
00:16:29,180 --> 00:16:31,060
truly only for me?

256
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:33,860
Stop deluding yourself, Chu Zhao.

257
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:36,380
I'm just

258
00:16:37,980 --> 00:16:40,540
a pretty excuse for your ambition.

259
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:02,340
You know what?

260
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:05,700
You're becoming another Xu Jingfu.

261
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:59,420
(Chu Mansion)

262
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:02,660
Miss Xu, your meal is served.

263
00:18:03,460 --> 00:18:04,820
Chu Zhao had you send these

264
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:06,740
for me to eat?

265
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:08,700
You're overthinking, Miss Xu.

266
00:18:08,940 --> 00:18:10,260
Our young master

267
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,260
is extremely busy.

268
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,980
He has no time to care about it.

269
00:18:15,300 --> 00:18:16,420
You wretched maid.

270
00:18:16,740 --> 00:18:17,580
You!

271
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:19,540
Still acting high and mighty?

272
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:20,620
Listen up.

273
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:22,060
His Majesty has decreed

274
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:23,580
a marriage between our young master

275
00:18:23,620 --> 00:18:24,460
and General Feihong.

276
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:26,060
Abandon your foolish hopes.

277
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,100
What did you say?

278
00:18:27,380 --> 00:18:29,020
Chu Zhao is marrying He Yan?

279
00:18:30,540 --> 00:18:31,580
Y-Yes.

280
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:33,180
The news has spread everywhere.

281
00:18:42,820 --> 00:18:43,700
No way.

282
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:45,300
Chu Zhao,

283
00:18:46,540 --> 00:18:47,900
you won't get your way.

284
00:19:01,420 --> 00:19:02,820
Have you met with Miss He?

285
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:04,740
How about

286
00:19:05,220 --> 00:19:06,060
your marriage?

287
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:08,500
There will be no marriage.

288
00:19:10,060 --> 00:19:10,980
Don't bring it up.

289
00:19:34,700 --> 00:19:36,780
I heard about
your imperial marriage decree

290
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:39,460
and came specially to congratulate you.

291
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:47,340
Why the haste, Mr. Chu?

292
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:52,300
I once thought

293
00:19:52,860 --> 00:19:54,980
only fools like me

294
00:19:55,740 --> 00:19:57,300
